To run specs mocked:
  rvm use 1.8.7
  bundle
  bundle exec rake

To run against tresfiestas codebase:
  rvm use 1.9.2
  BUNDLE_GEMFILE=InternalGemfile bundle
  BUNDLE_GEMFILE=InternalGemfile bundle exec rake

CI should:
  rvm use 1.9.2
  BUNDLE_GEMFILE=InternalGemfile bundle
  BUNDLE_GEMFILE=InternalGemfile bundle exec rake
  rvm use 1.8.7
  bundle
  bundle exec rake
